First time:
---------------
xubuntu@Xubuntu-VirtualBox:~/GitHub/Login_And_Session_Python$ python3 -m venv AUTH
xubuntu@Xubuntu-VirtualBox:~/GitHub/Login_And_Session_Python$ source AUTH/bin/activate
(AUTH) xubuntu@Xubuntu-VirtualBox:~/GitHub/Login_And_Session_Python$ 

To use again:
----------------
xubuntu@Xubuntu-VirtualBox:~/GitHub/Login_And_Session_Python$ ls
AUTH
xubuntu@Xubuntu-VirtualBox:~/GitHub/Login_And_Session_Python$ source AUTH/bin/activate
(AUTH) xubuntu@Xubuntu-VirtualBox:~/GitHub/Login_And_Session_Python$ 
